Class AbstractRMNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.rmnode.AbstractRMNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RMNode>, RMNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RMDeployingNode, RMNodeImpl

    public abstract class AbstractRMNode
extends Object
implements RMNode, Serializable
    Defines abstractions common to all RM node implementations.

      • isLocked

        protected volatile boolean isLocked
        Status associated to a ProActive Node. When a Node is locked, it is no longer eligible for Tasks execution. A ProActive node can be locked whatever its state is.

      • lastEvent

        protected RMNodeEvent lastEvent
        The last event

      • lockedBy
